  Bills after filtering: 2,234
  Firms after filtering: 294

  E[shared bills | median pair] = k_med²/B = 10.0² / 2234 = 0.045
  E[shared bills | mean pair]   = k_mean²/B = 21.0² / 2234 = 0.197

-- Step 4: Observed Edge Weights (filtered affiliation network) --
  Observed edges:       8,008
  Possible edges:       72,390
  Network density:      0.111  (11.1%)
